import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';
import { userUid } from 'src/app/login/login.page';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-tab1',
  templateUrl: 'tab1.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['tab1.page.scss']
})
export class Tab1Page implements OnInit{


  uid: string = userUid ;
  

  constructor() {}

  ngOnInit() {
  }

}
<ion-header [translucent]="true">
  <ion-toolbar>
 
    <ion-item large class="right" routerLink="/profil">
    <ion-icon name="person-circle-outline" ></ion-icon>
  </ion-item>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content [fullscreen]="true">
  <ion-header collapse="condense">
    <ion-toolbar>
      <ion-title size="large"></ion-title>
    </ion-toolbar>
  </ion-header>


  <ion-grid>
    <ion-row>
      <ion-col>
        <ion-card color="primary">
          <ion-card-header>
            <ion-card-title>Mes Dépenses</ion-card-title>
            <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
          </ion-card-header>
       
          <ion-card-content> 128.000 dinar</ion-card-content>
        </ion-card>
      </ion-col>
    </ion-row>
    <ion-row>
    <ion-col>
  <ion-card class="couleur2" routerLink="/medecin">
    <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title>Mes Médecins</ion-card-title>
      <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
    </ion-card-header>
  
    <ion-card-content>  </ion-card-content>
  </ion-card>
</ion-col>


<ion-col>
  <ion-card class="couleur2" routerLink="/document">
    <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title>Mes Documents</ion-card-title>
      <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
    </ion-card-header>
 
    <ion-card-content> </ion-card-content>
  </ion-card>
</ion-col>
</ion-row>

<ion-row>
  <ion-col>
  <ion-card class="couleur2" routerLink="/medicament">
    <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title >Mes Médicaments</ion-card-title>
      <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
    </ion-card-header>
  
    <ion-card-content> </ion-card-content>
  </ion-card>
</ion-col>
<ion-col>
  <ion-card class="couleur2">
    <ion-card-header>
      <ion-card-title>Ma sécurite sociale</ion-card-title>
      <ion-card-subtitle></ion-card-subtitle>
    </ion-card-header>
    <ion-card-content></ion-card-content>
    
  </ion-card>
</ion-col>
</ion-row>
</ion-grid>


</ion-content>
<ion-footer collapse="fade">
  <ion-toolbar>
  <ion-tabs>
    <ion-tab-bar slot="bottom">
      <ion-tab-button tab="home">
        <ion-icon name="home-outline" [routerLink]="uid ? '/tabs/tab1' : '/homeindividu'"></ion-icon>
        Home
      </ion-tab-button>
      <ion-tab-button tab="radio">
        <ion-icon name="calendar-outline" routerLink="/tabs/tab2"></ion-icon>
        Rendez-vous
      </ion-tab-button>
      <ion-tab-button tab="search">
        <ion-icon name="pin-outline" routerLink="/tabs/tab3"></ion-icon>
        A remplir
      </ion-tab-button>
    </ion-tab-bar>
  </ion-tabs>
</ion-toolbar>
</ion-footer>
